org.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.lft < 6 AND projects.rgt > 7 AND projects.status <> 9 AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (7, 12)) ORDER BY projects.lft ASC
